      <ol>
        <li>
          <strong>Book Your Appointment</strong>
          <br />
          Call or schedule online. We’ll confirm your preferred time and gather basic info about your appliance.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>On-Time Arrival & Brand-Specific Diagnosis</strong>
          <br />
          Your trained ZARICCI technician arrives promptly and performs a detailed inspection using specialized diagnostic tools.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Clear, Upfront Estimate</strong>
          <br />
          We walk you through the issue and provide a transparent quote—no pressure, no surprises.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Precision Repair Using OEM Parts</strong>
          <br />
          We complete the repair using authentic parts, restore function, and run comprehensive performance testing.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Final Walkthrough & Service Warranty</strong>
          <br />
          We clean up, answer your questions, and back our work with a warranty—because confidence is part of the experience.
        </li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Trusted Across Manhattan Beach’s Coastal Neighborhoods</h3>

      <p>
        We serve Manhattan Beach residences near The Strand and throughout the Sand Section, Tree Section, Hill Section, East Manhattan Beach, Manhattan Village, Manhattan Beach Heights, Liberty Village, and the surrounding residential neighborhoods. Our service is designed for beachfront homes, walk-street residences, ocean-view properties, remodeled coastal houses, and custom kitchens where careful diagnostics, clean workmanship, and discretion matter.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Your Home Deserves More Than a Quick Fix</h3>

